Use: Flip to the next section.

 (1 Sec Cooldown)

Equip: You are one of the devout. Your spells and abilities have a chance to grant you 2,088 Haste for 15 sec.

In addition, you grant another devout ally 418 Haste for 15 sec.

Use: Become Mudborne, absorbing 8.3 million damage and pulsing 410,795 Nature damage split between nearby enemies over 10 sec.

Periodic damage you take coalesces into pungent mud to feed the ritual, reducing this cooldown by 2.0 sec. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Being one of the devout grants an additional 261 Agility.
